 other hepatotoxic agents, and vice versa.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/15291/', '', 'Brivaracetam, Topiramate, Ezogabine, Lamotrigine, Lacosamide, Levetiracetam, Ethotoin, Paramethadione, Perampanel, Ganaxolone, Vigabatrin, More', 'Romiplostim, Avatrombopag, Emicizumab, Coagulation factor VIIa Recombinant Human, Coagulation factor X human, Phylloquinone, Lusutrombopag, Anti-inhibitor coagulant complex, Antihemophilic factor, human recombinant, Fibrinogen human, Epinephrine, Coagulation Factor IX Human', 1767369485);
